## Latino Isolation


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
nyc_race |> 
  mutate(interaction_bw = (HispanicE / co_HispanicE * HispanicE / PoptotE)) |>  
  group_by(Borough) |>
  summarise(interaction = sum(interaction_bw, na.rm=TRUE)) |> 
  gt()
```

